# The DECRYPTED keystore is transient (CI decrypts app/signing.p12.enc into it
# with the SIGNING_STORE_KEY secret) — never commit the plaintext keystore.
# The committed app/signing.p12.enc is AES-encrypted and safe to track.
app/signing.p12
*.jks
*.keystore
signing.p12.base64.txt
store_key.txt
